{"tid":2401711,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"土瓜灣僑裕大廈僑發大廈受限區域無發現確診個案","createTime":"2021-02-10T02:57:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T09:16:07.000Z","uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c2cfa908b8577c7d615d84689c50ba7ecf4536","tid":2401711,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T02:57:05.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣落山道的僑裕大廈及僑發大廈兩個「受限區域」的執法行動今早約10時完結，截至凌晨2時，約1700名居民接受檢測，當中沒有發現確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n政府呼籲沒有應門的30多戶居民，看到政府張貼的告示後，盡快聯絡政府並進行檢查，以排除病毒在小區內可能有機會繼續傳播的風險。<br />\n<br />\n在這次行動中，政府動員多個部門共約630人，安排強制檢測並進行執法。"},{"pid":"bf40ca8832e0a83fcc0b7046bf3d96dd93cae88e","tid":2401711,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T02:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1575075_1_L_20210210103933.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1575075_1_L_20210210103933.jpg&h=7a69f665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又食白果呀~"},{"pid":"6c5f8dd94578ff7f4b9d04b5053a7a1cc69d50bf","tid":2401711,"uid":268591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T09:16:07.000Z","msg":"失敗完一次又一次<br />\n做Show唔使本"}]}